{"tid":1018983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門貪污案大劉羅傑承判囚63個月 將來...","createTime":"2019-02-12T15:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T18:28:14.000Z","uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ed5d3db2ba305a5edec2c2317565cc3f35bfbd","tid":1018983,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"澳門初級法院經過近兩年審訊，昨宣判華置主席「大劉」劉鑾雄及南華足主羅傑承，行賄澳門運輸工務司前司長歐文龍及洗黑錢罪名成立，劉、羅各判監禁五年三個月。案中八名被告全部缺席聽審，大劉女友呂麗君出席旁聽，劉、羅代表律師表示會提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140315/18657189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140315%2F18657189&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIumzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=800ad502\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140315%2F18657189&h=a411064e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140315/18657189</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8290b56f720488400198d583bedcfafcb4340564","tid":1018983,"uid":213762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebcdf273d97b8fc464cb6ac3c76a941f1dbd4b2c","tid":1018983,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"777借台灣單野震懾富豪"},{"pid":"f8c954250250d7c85207a3c457363b109f57676f","tid":1018983,"uid":162295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"有錢佬真係好貪"},{"pid":"e2fce6fd50664a0a4759ce225aafb8a02ef4bc45","tid":1018983,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"劉鑾雄及南華足主羅傑承將被一次性<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">移</span></span>交澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f91c9da97ed30bf9728519afc9047d2adac863","